                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Madame <persName type="from">Chiang Kai-shek</persName> to Mr.
                            <persName type="to">Lauchlin Currie</persName>
                    </hi>
                    <note n="23" type="source" xml:id="d72fn23">Copy of telegram transmitted to
                        President Roosevelt. Photostatic copy obtained from the Franklin D.
                        Roosevelt Library, Hyde Park, N. Y.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Chungking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1942-05-31">May 31,
                            1942</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Owing critical situation in China theater Generalissimo wiring President request
                    Hopkins come China for consultation. Would it be feasible for you to come
                    together. Reply immediately.</p>
            </div>
